Package org.neo4j.token

Class TokenRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.token.TokenRegistry
  • public class TokenRegistry
extends Object
    Token registry provide id -> TOKEN and name -> id mappings. Name -> id mapping will be updated last since it's used to check if the token already exists. Implementation guarantees the atomicity of each method using internal locking.
